      "description": "Get ready for your next rewarding project! This vehicle is the perfect canvas for a dedicated restorer or a fantastic source of quality parts. While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to get back on the road, it offers a wonderful opportunity for someone with the skills and passion to bring a classic back to its former glory!",
