    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! It honestly breaks my heart a little to even think about letting this beauty go. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014always garage-kept, hand-washed every weekend, and it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s in absolutely stunning condition, inside and out; you won't find a speck of dust in the cabin or a smudge on the paint. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been treated with nothing but love and is ready for a new home, this is the one. Come by, let's chat cars, and I'll get you behind the wheel of your dream ride!",
      "price": 48500.0,
