    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a surgically precise specimen for the discerning driver. This machine features a meticulously blueprinted power plant with optimized compression ratios and a flawlessly mapped ECU for instantaneous throttle response. The chassis is fully dialed, utilizing a high-performance coilover system and reinforced subframe bushings to eliminate lateral deflection. Every shift through the close-ratio gearbox is crisp, and the drivetrain remains utterly bulletproof under load. The exterior boasts a deep, multi-stage ceramic finish over factory-perfect panels, ensuring the drag coefficient remains as intended. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a mechanically superior vehicle that has been maintained to an obsessive standard. Zero fluid migration, no vacuum leaks, and a power-to-weight ratio that dominates the tarmac.",
      "price": 48900.0,
